&lt;h1 id="how-to-work-hard"&gt;How to Work Hard&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;June 2021&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It might not seem there&amp;rsquo;s much to learn about how to work hard. Anyone who&amp;rsquo;s been to school knows what it entails, even if they chose not to do it. There are 12 year olds who work amazingly hard. And yet when I ask if I know more about working hard now than when I was in school, the answer is definitely yes.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>The Anatomy of Determination</title><link>https://linguista.cn/person/paul_graham/essays_en/determination/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/person/paul_graham/essays_en/determination/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;→ &lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/person/paul_graham/essays_zh/determination/"&gt;Chinese Version&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
